data.description: REDUCED!! SPACIOUS 3bed/2bath FULL BASEMENT home on .58 acres in popular Norris Lake community with a 90 acre lake, pool and tennis courts. Perfect place to enjoy swimming, fishing, water-skiing, jet-skiing and tennis. Lots of parks nearby and close to schools and shopping. Beautiful wooded views and a relaxing creek in the backyard. The great room and kitchen are great for get togethers. The home has a full basement with finished areas and a large 2 car garage. Call now to find out more details! Appointment only!
